description: Gourmet Provisions International Corporation franchises pizza and sub restaurants in the United States. Its restaurants offer pizzas, subs, calzones, salads, and beverages. The company also provides an express franchise for carts/kiosks; and retail franchises for retailers. The company was formerly known as Unique Foods Corporation and changed its name to Gourmet Provisions International Corporation in November 2020. Gourmet Provisions International Corporation is based in Trafford, Pennsylvania.
